rewrite, need to use it on the offer letter:: 1.	All stated monetary figures are gross amounts (before tax), and are paid in monthly deposits in Chinese RMB.
** Note 2：
Please be assured all your submitted documents are authentic and valid, and you will agree to accept the job criteria set by our kindergarten when joining. Any of the following circumstances shall be considered as invalid and the kindergarten has the right not to sign the employment contract or to terminate it immediately:
1)	False application information or onboard documents is provided;
2)	Serious violations of professional ethics have been found;
3)	Fail to provide required materials for onboarding within specified dates, and do not onboard on the above specified onboard date;
4)	Above position has been cancelled or adjusted due to changes of company's business and staffing plan.

To accept this offer, please reply to us within 3 days. If we do not hear back from you by 12:00 a.m. of 2nd June 2023, the offer will be expired automatically and we will proceed with our alternative candidate. If you have any questions or misunderstandings about this offer, please feel free to contact the HR department at <PRESIDIO_ANONYMIZED_EMAIL_ADDRESS>.
